    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary, and if you like your steak well-done, it may take you a little longer than 10 min</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/steak-with-charred-corn-rice-and-spicy-mayo/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat two dry, large, wide-based pans (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Pat the\u00a0<strong>rump steaks</strong>\u00a0dry with\u00a0kitchen\u00a0paper,\u00a0drizzle with\u00a0<strong>vegetable oil</strong>\u00a0and season all over with\u00a0<strong>salt</strong>\u00a0and\u00a0<strong>pepper</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/steak-with-charred-corn-rice-and-spicy-mayo/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once very hot, add the\u00a0<strong>seasoned</strong> <strong>steaks</strong>\u00a0to one of the pans</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side</p><p>For<strong> </strong>medium-rare, cook for 2-3 min on each side</p><p>For\u00a0medium, cook for 3-4 min on each side</p><p>Once the steaks are cooked, transfer them to a plate to rest</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/steak-with-charred-corn-rice-and-spicy-mayo/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add a generous knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the other pan</p><p>Drain the<strong> sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until golden brown \u2013 this is your <strong>buttery corn</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/steak-with-charred-corn-rice-and-spicy-mayo/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> mayo</strong>, <strong>sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chilli jam</strong> in a bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>spicy mayo</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/steak-with-charred-corn-rice-and-spicy-mayo/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>steamed\u00a0white\u00a0basmati rice</strong> to the buttery corn and cook for 2-3 min further or until warmed through \u2013 this is your <strong>charred</strong> <strong>corn rice</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/steak-with-charred-corn-rice-and-spicy-mayo/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>\u00a0with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong>\u00a0and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a small bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>vinaigrette</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>lamb's lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/steak-with-charred-corn-rice-and-spicy-mayo/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested</strong> <strong>steaks</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> sliced steaks </strong>with the<strong>\u00a0charred corn rice </strong>and<strong> lamb's lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> spicy mayo</strong> over the<strong> </strong>steak and the<strong> vinaigrette</strong>\u00a0all over the<strong> </strong>lettuce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
